HEADWORD: Bridgeing
<hw>Bridge"ing</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Arch.)</fld>
<def>The system of bracing used between floor or other timbers to
distribute the weight.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Bridging joist</b></col>. <cd>Same as <er>Binding
joist</er>.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Bridgey</ent>⟦br⟧
